text: Taturru itte ummattak ummaan ummatah le madqa madaqneeh usun woo madqal taamitan,, toysa Nabiyow makki koros islaam diinih madqaa kee qibaadak Yalli koo kah amrissi heemil koo keemaarise woonay, kaadu ku- Rabbi inkittoysaanam kee qibaadá kaah caglisaanamal sinaamah sec, diggah atu massale gitay makó aalle waah bagul tanik
